NAME:
  ResourceInclude ( index ; urlOnly )

PURPOSE:
  Wraps text or url from Resource record with specified index in HTML include statement.

EXAMPLES:
  
  
DEPENDENCIES:
  Custom Functions: PathEncodeForWebViewer ( )
  Fields: FOCUS fields that store RESOURCE data

